                                                </div>
                                                <div class="col-md-6 mb-30">
                                                    <p class="mb-15">Our team of skilled doctors...</p>
                                                    <div class="checklist body-color">
                                                        <ul>
                                                            <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Minimal sedation – you are awake but relaxed</li>
                                                            <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Deep sedation – 24/7 care for mother and baby</li>
